<title>USA: Hughes unit gets $111 mln army contract.</title>
<headline>Hughes unit gets $111 mln army contract.</headline>
<dateline>EL SEGUNDO, Calif 1997-04-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>Hughes Aircraft Co, a unit of Hughes Electronics Corp, said it was awarded a $111 million multi-year contract for second generation infrared imaging upgrade kits that will provide significantly greater night time performance for U.S. Army combat vehicles.</p>
<p>The annually funded production contract has first year funding of $12.9 million.</p>
<p>The contract is for the Horizontal Technology Integrations second generation forward-looking infrared program, Hughes said.</p>
